570
00:40:51.448 --> 00:40:55.149
That moron. All she did was work nonstop.

571
00:41:25.778 --> 00:41:26.888
Jung Hee.

572
00:41:27.988 --> 00:41:31.758
I wanted to see you before I left,

573
00:41:32.618 --> 00:41:33.959
but I just left.

574
00:41:35.928 --> 00:41:38.899
I was happy living with my kind...

575
00:41:39.258 --> 00:41:41.028
and pretty Jung Hee.

576
00:41:42.298 --> 00:41:43.328
That's right.

577
00:41:43.839 --> 00:41:46.908
I left you a gift in the closet.

578
00:41:49.638 --> 00:41:51.408
I made it.

579
00:41:52.678 --> 00:41:54.408
I hope you like it.

580
00:42:00.089 --> 00:42:01.149
Jung Hee.

581
00:42:02.988 --> 00:42:05.189
Grow up to be a beautiful girl.

582
00:42:05.718 --> 00:42:06.959
Be proud.

583
00:42:08.488 --> 00:42:09.758
Love, Auntie.

584
00:42:55.238 --> 00:42:56.738
Are you leaving?

