595
00:43:36.408 --> 00:43:37.519
I will.

596
00:43:38.348 --> 00:43:40.388
If that's what you want,

597
00:43:40.888 --> 00:43:41.948
I will.

598
00:43:45.319 --> 00:43:47.089
