599
00:43:48.028 --> 00:43:49.689
but I'll try.

600
00:44:32.098 --> 00:44:33.339
How will you live?

601
00:44:35.008 --> 00:44:36.339
It doesn't matter...

602
00:44:36.908 --> 00:44:38.609
to you anymore.

603
00:44:43.778 --> 00:44:44.879
Are you sure...

604
00:44:46.278 --> 00:44:47.448
