605
00:44:48.919 --> 00:44:50.859
Won't you regret taking off with me?

606
00:44:51.359 --> 00:44:53.428
Why would I when I'm with you?

607
00:44:54.828 --> 00:44:56.859
If I'm with you,

608
00:44:57.629 --> 00:44:58.899
why would I?

609
00:45:22.348 --> 00:45:24.658
Don't leave me behind.

610
00:45:28.689 --> 00:45:30.158
Don't leave me.

611
00:45:35.428 --> 00:45:36.798
I love you, Hae Joo.

612
00:45:53.348 --> 00:45:54.348
Okay.

613
00:46:01.028 --> 00:46:02.629
Give it to me.

614
00:46:06.298 --> 00:46:07.499
Let's go, Eng Cho.

615
00:46:10.198 --> 00:46:12.439
Sit at the front with Eng Cho.

616
00:46:12.439 --> 00:46:14.138
I'll sit here.

617
00:46:15.069 --> 00:46:16.839
I'll sit here too.

618
00:46:20.149 --> 00:46:21.149
It's finished.

619
00:46:21.149 --> 00:46:23.078
Okay. Thanks.

620
00:46:23.309 --> 00:46:25.249
- Thank you. - I appreciate it.

621
00:46:26.919 --> 00:46:29.718
Hae Joo. When you settle down,

622
00:46:30.089 --> 00:46:31.158
make sure to contact me.

623
00:46:31.158 --> 00:46:32.419
Of course.

624
00:46:33.158 --> 00:46:34.359
Hey,

625
00:46:34.428 --> 00:46:36.189
you better be good to Hae Joo.

626
00:46:36.189 --> 00:46:37.859
I'll be watching you.

627
00:46:37.859 --> 00:46:40.229
I'm so scared of you.

628
00:46:43.539 --> 00:46:44.539
Don't worry.

629
00:46:45.638 --> 00:46:47.039
I'll take good care of her.

630
00:46:55.278 --> 00:46:56.379
Take care.

631
00:47:01.419 --> 00:47:04.089
Thank you, my friend.

632
00:47:14.528 --> 00:47:16.198
- We're leaving. - Okay.

633
00:47:21.939 --> 00:47:23.339
Don't get sick.

634
00:47:23.908 --> 00:47:25.039
Stay healthy.

635
00:47:58.539 --> 00:47:59.709
Stop crying.

636
00:48:00.778 --> 00:48:02.078
Hae Joo will be fine.

637
00:48:03.149 --> 00:48:04.249
I'm not crying.

638
00:48:05.919 --> 00:48:07.189
I know that.

639
00:48:07.988 --> 00:48:09.519
Hae Joo will be fine.

640
00:48:12.289 --> 00:48:13.289
Park Hae Joo.

641
00:48:13.559 --> 00:48:15.629
It was her dream...

642
00:48:15.758 --> 00:48:16.999
to fall in a passionate love.

643
00:48:18.428 --> 00:48:19.559
Her dream came true.

644
00:48:20.999 --> 00:48:22.069
What about you?

645
00:48:22.868 --> 00:48:24.238
What was your dream?

646
00:48:28.109 --> 00:48:29.169
Son Jin?

647
00:48:29.908 --> 00:48:31.379
You little...

648
00:48:32.638 --> 00:48:34.348
You little...

649
00:48:36.249 --> 00:48:37.749
Since you're feeling down,

650
00:48:38.218 --> 00:48:40.988
