651
00:48:41.789 --> 00:48:44.388
Today's show would be sold out already.

652
00:48:44.388 --> 00:48:45.559
It's Sunday.

653
00:48:46.189 --> 00:48:48.658
I already got us tickets.

654
00:48:50.729 --> 00:48:53.468
Wow. Bae Dong Moon.

655
00:48:53.798 --> 00:48:54.928
Also,

656
00:48:55.428 --> 00:48:58.269
I'm going to start officially.

657
00:48:58.368 --> 00:48:59.468
Start what?

658
00:49:02.039 --> 00:49:03.439
Being your boyfriend.

659
00:49:05.238 --> 00:49:06.278
This is...

660
00:49:06.638 --> 00:49:09.348
considered the first step.

661
00:49:10.178 --> 00:49:11.379
Who says?

662
00:49:12.218 --> 00:49:13.218
Bye.

663
00:49:16.118 --> 00:49:18.718
Anyway, if you show up,

664
00:49:19.059 --> 00:49:20.629
I'll consider that you agree.

665
00:49:20.828 --> 00:49:22.129
I'll become your boyfriend.

666
00:49:22.828 --> 00:49:24.428
Go away.

667
00:49:26.968 --> 00:49:29.069
See you later, Jung Hee.

668
00:49:43.649 --> 00:49:45.718
Who says you can be my boyfriend?

669
00:49:49.289 --> 00:49:50.289
Jung Hee.

670
00:49:52.988 --> 00:49:54.028
Jin.

671
00:49:54.758 --> 00:49:56.359
What are you doing here?

672
00:49:56.798 --> 00:49:58.828
Oh. Well...

673
00:49:58.828 --> 00:50:01.069
What do we do?

674
00:50:01.069 --> 00:50:02.828
Hae Joo already left.

675
00:50:03.499 --> 00:50:04.569
Really?

676
00:50:05.999 --> 00:50:08.209
Did she leave today?

677
00:50:10.408 --> 00:50:11.508
I didn't know.

678
00:50:15.649 --> 00:50:16.649
Did the move...

679
00:50:17.548 --> 00:50:18.649
go well?

680
00:50:19.319 --> 00:50:20.319
Yes.

681
00:50:21.089 --> 00:50:23.019
Well... Then...

682
00:50:23.519 --> 00:50:25.559
Did you come on family business?

683
00:50:26.158 --> 00:50:27.158
I...

684
00:50:28.189 --> 00:50:29.388
missed you.

685
00:50:31.959 --> 00:50:33.769
I came because I missed you.

686
00:50:36.298 --> 00:50:38.899
But it's already getting late.

687
00:50:39.569 --> 00:50:40.638
What should I do?

688
00:50:40.968 --> 00:50:42.939
Did you wait a long time?

689
00:50:43.309 --> 00:50:46.109
I was helping Hae Joo with her move.

690
00:50:46.138 --> 00:50:47.278
Did you?

691
00:50:48.149 --> 00:50:49.309
Good job.

692
00:51:01.189 --> 00:51:02.589
For some reason,

693
00:51:04.359 --> 00:51:06.359
I kept thinking about you while in Seoul.

694
00:51:07.069 --> 00:51:08.528
Then I realized...

695
00:51:10.399 --> 00:51:11.468
that I...

696
00:51:12.968 --> 00:51:15.868
started to like you.

697
00:51:20.408 --> 00:51:21.448
Jung Hee.

698
00:51:23.249 --> 00:51:24.578
If it's not too late,

699
00:51:26.519 --> 00:51:30.089
will you accept my feelings?

700
00:51:35.359 --> 00:51:36.388
Were you surprised?

701
00:51:37.328 --> 00:51:38.499
I'm sure you are.

702
00:51:43.638 --> 00:51:45.499
I have to drop by home.

703
00:51:46.908 --> 00:51:48.669
I have a ticket for the bus at 4pm.

704
00:51:49.408 --> 00:51:52.408
Can I see you before I go?

705
00:51:56.348 --> 00:51:57.678
The 4pm bus?

706
00:51:59.749 --> 00:52:01.919
I'll wait for you at the terminal.

707
00:52:07.388 --> 00:52:09.658
(Showtime: 4pm)

708
00:52:10.158 --> 00:52:12.528
Why does everything...

709
00:52:12.959 --> 00:52:15.198
come to you a step too late?

710
00:53:53.868 --> 00:53:54.968
Jung Hee.

711
00:53:58.439 --> 00:53:59.499
I'm sorry.

712
00:54:01.939 --> 00:54:05.078
The film is starting. Please come in.

713
00:54:27.328 --> 00:54:30.638
The 4pm bus to Seoul is departing soon. Get on.

714
00:54:48.289 --> 00:54:49.319
Jung Hee.

715
00:55:03.839 --> 00:55:05.069
Aren't you going in?

716
00:55:05.499 --> 00:55:07.908
- Pardon? - It's starting soon.

717
00:55:28.859 --> 00:55:32.098
Jung Hee. Are you not coming?

718
00:55:33.359 --> 00:55:34.999
I guess you don't like me.

719
00:56:21.479 --> 00:56:22.578
Is this...

720
00:56:23.879 --> 00:56:25.178
how it's going to end?

721
00:56:25.749 --> 00:56:28.749
What are you doing? The film is over.

722
00:56:30.048 --> 00:56:32.388
I'm leaving.

723
00:56:33.118 --> 00:56:34.488
I'll leave.

724
00:56:37.629 --> 00:56:38.629
Jung Hee.

725
00:56:40.298 --> 00:56:42.669
Dong Moon. Is that where you were?

726
00:56:48.539 --> 00:56:49.569
Jung Hee.

727
00:56:53.948 --> 00:56:54.979
When did you get here?

728
00:56:55.048 --> 00:56:57.149
I was a little late,

729
00:56:57.448 --> 00:56:59.448
so I couldn't find my seat and sat here.

730
00:56:59.548 --> 00:57:00.988
My neck hurts.

731
00:57:04.658 --> 00:57:05.789
Jung Hee.

732
00:57:07.629 --> 00:57:08.789
Thank you.

733
00:57:14.629 --> 00:57:16.098
Thank you so much.

734
00:57:17.399 --> 00:57:19.939
What's wrong with you? Let me go.

735
00:57:29.948 --> 00:57:30.979
Jung Hee.

736
00:57:34.319 --> 00:57:35.388
Bae Dong Moon.

737
00:57:37.019 --> 00:57:38.158
You won.

738
00:57:51.169 --> 00:57:54.138
I thought you weren't coming.

739
00:57:56.339 --> 00:57:57.778
Why wouldn't I?

740
00:57:58.109 --> 00:57:59.578
It'd be a waste of a movie ticket.

741
00:58:00.479 --> 00:58:02.149
Is that why you came?

742
00:58:03.249 --> 00:58:04.618
Didn't you come for me?

743
00:58:06.249 --> 00:58:07.289
No.

744
00:58:11.319 --> 00:58:12.359
You did.

745
00:58:15.689 --> 00:58:16.928
Then...

746
00:58:19.698 --> 00:58:21.499
Well...

747
00:58:22.968 --> 00:58:25.939
I started to like Dong Moon.

748
00:58:29.169 --> 00:58:32.039
I'm sorry, Jin.

749
00:58:34.908 --> 00:58:36.149
Don't be sorry.

750
00:58:37.819 --> 00:58:39.419
People...

751
00:58:40.618 --> 00:58:42.149
change minds all the time.

752
00:58:45.258 --> 00:58:46.388
Just like...

753
00:58:47.158 --> 00:58:48.229
how my heart...

754
00:58:49.758 --> 00:58:51.298
turned towards you.

755
00:59:03.269 --> 00:59:04.439
Right?

756
00:59:06.278 --> 00:59:09.048
No. I really didn't.

757
00:59:11.078 --> 00:59:12.149
You're...

758
00:59:12.979 --> 00:59:14.519
giving me the permission, right?

759
00:59:15.218 --> 00:59:16.758
As your boyfriend?

760
00:59:18.988 --> 00:59:21.129
- Maybe. - What do you mean maybe?

761
00:59:22.258 --> 00:59:24.258
I can see it on your face.

762
00:59:25.028 --> 00:59:26.899
Nothing is on my face.

763
00:59:28.968 --> 00:59:30.069
It's written all over.

764
00:59:30.399 --> 00:59:32.399
"Yes, let's do that."

765
00:59:32.899 --> 00:59:34.238
That's what it says.

766
00:59:35.368 --> 00:59:36.609
You're a liar.

767
00:59:44.118 --> 00:59:46.178
Hey, Dong Moon.

768
00:59:48.988 --> 00:59:50.118
Jung Hee.

769
00:59:54.828 --> 00:59:56.559
I really, really like you.

770
01:00:18.078 --> 01:00:19.218
Jung Hee.

771
01:00:27.928 --> 01:00:29.258
Wait for me.

772
01:00:29.528 --> 01:00:30.629
I don't want to.

773
01:00:30.999 --> 01:00:33.359
- Let's walk together. - I don't want to.

774
01:00:34.098 --> 01:00:36.069
Don't be mad. Come on.

775
01:00:36.229 --> 01:00:37.298
All right.

776
01:00:38.198 --> 01:00:40.039
- Do you want steamed bun? - Steamed buns?

777
01:00:40.109 --> 01:00:42.039
Yes. No?

778
01:00:50.879 --> 01:00:52.178
Eun Ja,

779
01:00:52.948 --> 01:00:54.649
- I love you. - Are you crazy?

780
01:00:54.649 --> 01:00:55.689
I love you.

781
01:00:55.689 --> 01:00:56.888
- I'm crazy about you. - What are you saying?

782
01:00:56.888 --> 01:00:59.819
Roses? Daisies? You look like them all.

783
01:00:59.819 --> 01:01:01.658
- I'll tattle to Jung Hee. - Go ahead!

784
01:01:01.658 --> 01:01:02.859
What's wrong?

785
01:01:07.428 --> 01:01:08.528
Suk Hee.

786
01:01:19.638 --> 01:01:20.778
Please take them.

787
01:01:31.618 --> 01:01:35.789
(Thank you for watching Girls' Generation 1979.)

788
01:01:39.129 --> 01:01:40.499
Please be happy,

789
01:01:40.968 --> 01:01:42.198
Young Choon.

790
01:02:12.559 --> 01:02:13.928
